{"tw": {"4030000": {"success": true, "data": {"type": "game", "name": "Goddess of Death", "steam_appid": 4030000, "required_age": 0, "is_free": false, "controller_support": "full", "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在一個被殭屍蹂躪、文明徹底崩壞的末日世界中，你是人類最後的倖存男人——體內承載著唯一的解藥：你強大的種子。與一群魅力十足的倖存者並肩作戰，在這款動作感滿載的生存射擊遊戲中努力求生。與亡靈交戰、守護同伴，讓慾望與絕望交織，每一個選擇都將塑造人類最後的生存希望。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>白晝防線 — 無盡浪潮</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4030000/extras/8a8d80e1dcedd9ed82a9ef0f2d91c1a1.poster.avif?t=1772762896\" width=780 height=438 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4030000/extras/8a8d80e1dcedd9ed82a9ef0f2d91c1a1.webm?t=1772762896\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4030000/extras/8a8d80e1dcedd9ed82a9ef0f2d91c1a1.mp4?t=1772762896\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >當太陽升起，無情的殭屍浪潮朝你的基地湧來，生存仰賴火力、默契，以及對特殊技能的巧妙運用。你將指揮站在前線的女主角們。親自操控她們躲進掩體、在高壓中重新站位、精準射擊，並啟動足以扭轉戰局的獨特能力。每一天，都是一場守護人類最後據點的緊張激戰。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>夜間行動 — 準備與搜刮</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4030000/extras/78846b1c63d9dda4053cec22c1884c82.poster.avif?t=1772762896\" width=780 height=438 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4030000/extras/78846b1c63d9dda4053cec22c1884c82.webm?t=1772762896\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4030000/extras/78846b1c63d9dda4053cec22c1884c82.mp4?t=1772762896\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >夜幕降臨，你返回基地為即將到來的挑戰做好準備。升級武器與裝備、強化防禦工事，並自訂女孩們的服裝。隨後，在黑暗的掩護下，你派遣一名選定的女主角外出搜刮。再次親自操控她，穿梭於危險的建築之中，擊退潛伏的殭屍，蒐集撐過下一天所需的珍貴資源。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4030000/extras/d8bed79a54bbdd032ee329639199619d.poster.avif?t=1772762896\" width=780 height=438 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4030000/extras/d8bed79a54bbdd032ee329639199619d.webm?t=1772762896\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4030000/extras/d8bed79a54bbdd032ee329639199619d.mp4?t=1772762896\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >但務必小心行事。在陰影之中，恐怖的Boss級殭屍正在廢墟中徘徊，它們比白天遭遇的任何敵人都更加致命。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4030000/extras/1d0bb2b990ee97ea09b473841fa51619.poster.avif?t=1772762896\" width=780 height=438 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4030000/extras/1d0bb2b990ee97ea09b473841fa51619.webm?t=1772762896\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4030000/extras/1d0bb2b990ee97ea09b473841fa51619.mp4?t=1772762896\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>親密與羈絆 — 人類最後的希望</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4030000/extras/ace1b587a831af434507ae1ae821fee1.poster.avif?t=1772762896\" width=780 height=438 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4030000/extras/ace1b587a831af434507ae1ae821fee1.webm?t=1772762896\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4030000/extras/ace1b587a831af434507ae1ae821fee1.mp4?t=1772762896\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在子彈與路障之外，才是這段旅程真正的核心。你將與那些把信任與未來託付給你的美麗倖存者共享親密時刻。在瀕臨滅絕的世界中，激情、連結，以及你獨一無二的解藥，將成為人類延續的最後火花。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4030000/extras/a3f717b8902b9aeee5657d6b1b57877e.poster.avif?t=1772762896\" width=780 height=438 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4030000/extras/a3f717b8902b9aeee5657d6b1b57877e.webm?t=1772762896\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4030000/extras/a3f717b8902b9aeee5657d6b1b57877e.mp4?t=1772762896\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>", "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在一個被殭屍蹂躪、文明徹底崩壞的末日世界中，你是人類最後的倖存男人——體內承載著唯一的解藥：你強大的種子。與一群魅力十足的倖存者並肩作戰，在這款動作感滿載的生存射擊遊戲中努力求生。與亡靈交戰、守護同伴，讓慾望與絕望交織，每一個選擇都將塑造人類最後的生存希望。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>白晝防線 — 無盡浪潮</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4030000/extras/8a8d80e1dcedd9ed82a9ef0f2d91c1a1.poster.avif?t=1772762896\" width=780 height=438 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4030000/extras/8a8d80e1dcedd9ed82a9ef0f2d91c1a1.webm?t=1772762896\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4030000/extras/8a8d80e1dcedd9ed82a9ef0f2d91c1a1.mp4?t=1772762896\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >當太陽升起，無情的殭屍浪潮朝你的基地湧來，生存仰賴火力、默契，以及對特殊技能的巧妙運用。你將指揮站在前線的女主角們。親自操控她們躲進掩體、在高壓中重新站位、精準射擊，並啟動足以扭轉戰局的獨特能力。每一天，都是一場守護人類最後據點的緊張激戰。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><str