deo/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4030000/extras/1d0bb2b990ee97ea09b473841fa51619.mp4?t=1772762896\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>親密與羈絆 — 人類最後的希望</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4030000/extras/ace1b587a831af434507ae1ae821fee1.poster.avif?t=1772762896\" width=780 height=438 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4030000/extras/ace1b587a831af434507ae1ae821fee1.webm?t=1772762896\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4030000/extras/ace1b587a831af434507ae1ae821fee1.mp4?t=1772762896\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在子彈與路障之外，才是這段旅程真正的核心。你將與那些把信任與未來託付給你的美麗倖存者共享親密時刻。在瀕臨滅絕的世界中，激情、連結，以及你獨一無二的解藥，將成為人類延續的最後火花。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4030000/extras/a3f717b8902b9aeee5657d6b1b57877e.poster.avif?t=1772762896\" width=780 height=438 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4030000/extras/a3f717b8902b9aeee5657d6b1b57877e.webm?t=1772762896\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4030000/extras/a3f717b8902b9aeee5657d6b1b57877e.mp4?t=1772762896\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>", "short_description": "殭屍蹂躪著末世世界，而你是最後的男人，懷揣唯一的解藥：你強大的種子。加入美麗的倖存者，在這款動作生存射擊遊戲中——守護你的基地，熬過無盡的黑夜，在白天搜尋資源，並與同伴沉醉於禁忌的親密之中。", "supported_languages": "英文, 日文<strong>*</strong>, 韓文, 簡體中文, 繁體中文, 俄文, 泰文<br><strong>*</strong>具備完整音效支援的語言", "header_image": "https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4030000/e9266b2805a179b3d774bdfb338ba095f7463896/header.jpg?t=1772762896", "capsule_image": "https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4030000/2ebf96932facb76722b368bd2d83cf349b98192d/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1772762896", "capsule_imagev5": "https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4030000/2ebf96932facb76722b368bd2d83cf349b98192d/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1772762896", "website": null, "pc_requirements": {"minimum": "<strong>最低配備:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>作業系統:</strong> Windows 10 or 11<br></li><li><strong>處理器:</strong> Intel Core i7-6700K<br></li><li><strong>記憶體:</strong> 4 GB 記憶體<br></li><li><strong>顯示卡:</strong> NVIDIA GeForce GTX 1070<br></li><li><strong>儲存空間:</strong> 2 GB 可用空間</li></ul>", "recommended": "<strong>建議配備:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>作業系統:</strong> Windows 10 or 11<br></li><li><strong>處理器:</strong> Intel Core i5-10400 / AMD Ryzen 5 3600<br></li><li><strong>記憶體:</strong> 16 GB 記憶體<br></li><li><strong>顯示卡:</strong> NVIDIA GeForce RTX 2060/ AMD Radeon RX 5700<br></li><li><strong>儲存空間:</strong> 2 GB 可用空間</li></ul>"}, "mac_requirements": [], "linux_requirements": [], "legal_notice": "2025 Tora Creatives", "release_date": {"coming_soon": true, "date": "2026 第 4 季"}}}}, "us": {"4030000": {"success": true, "data": {"type": "game", "name": "Goddess of Death", "steam_appid": 4030000, "required_age": 0, "is_free": false, "controller_support": "full", "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In a zombie-ravaged apocalypse where civilization has collapsed, you stand as humanity’s last surviving man—bearing the only cure within you: your potent seed. Alongside a group of alluring survivors, you must fight to endure in this action-packed survival shooter. Battle the undead, protect your companions, and let desire and desperation intertwine as every choice you make shapes humanity’s final chance at survival.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Daytime Defense — Relentless Waves</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4030000/extras/8a8d80e1dcedd9ed82a9ef0f2d91c1a1.poster.avif?t=1772762896\" width=780 height=438 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4030000/extras/8a8d80e1dcedd9ed82a9ef0f2d91c1a1.webm?t=1772762896\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4030000/extras/8a8d80e1dcedd9ed82a9ef0f2d91c1a1.mp4?t=1772762896\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >When the sun rises, waves of relentless zombies surge toward your base, and survival depends on firepower, coordination, and the smart use of special skills. It’s up to you to command the heroines on the front line. Take direct control as they duck behind barriers, reposition under pressure, unleash precise gunfire, and activate unique abilities that can turn the tide of battle. Each day becomes a tense, action-packed struggle to keep humanity’s last shelter standing.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Night Operations — Prepare and Scavenge</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4030000/extras/78846b1c63d9dda4053cec22c1884c82.poster.avif?t=1772762896\" width=780 height=438 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4030000/extras/78846b1c63d9dda4053cec22c1884c82.webm?t=1772762896\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4030000/extras/78846b1c63d9dda4053cec22c1884c82.mp4?t=1772762896\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >As night falls, you return to base to prepare for the challenges ahead. Upgrade weapons and gear, strengthen your defenses, and customize the girls’ outfits. Then, under the cover of darkness, you send a chosen heroine out to scavenge. Taking control once more, you guide her through dangerous buildings, fighting off lurking zombies and collecting precious resources needed to survive another day.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4030000/extras/d8bed79a54bbdd032ee329639199619d.poster.avif?t=1772762896\" width=780 height=438 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4030000/extras/d8bed79a54bbdd032ee329639199619d.webm?t=1772762896\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4030000/extras/d8bed79a54bbdd032ee329639199619d.mp4?t=1772762896\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >But proceed with caution. In the shadows, terrifying boss zombies roam the ruins, even far deadlier than anything you face during the day.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4030000/extras/1d0bb2b990ee97ea09b473841fa51619.poster.avif?t=1772762896\" width=780 height=438 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4030000/extras/1d0bb2b990ee97ea09b473841fa51619.webm?t=1772762896\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4030000/extras/1d0bb2b990ee97ea09b473841fa51619.mp4?t=1772762896\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Intimacy &amp; Bonds — Humanity’s Final Hope</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4030000/extras/ace1b587a831af434507ae1ae821fee1.poster.avif?t=1772762896\" width=780 height=438 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4030000/extras/ace1b587a831af434507ae1ae821fee1.webm?t=1772762896\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4030000/extras/ace1b587a831af434507ae1ae821fee1.mp4?t=1772762896\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Beyond bullets and barricades lies the heart of the journey. You share intimate moments with the beautiful survivors who have placed their trust—and their future—in you. In a world on the brink of extinction, passion, connection, and your unique cure become the final spark of hope for humanity’s survival.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4030000/extras/a3f717b8902b9aeee5657d6b1b57877e.poster.avif?t=1772762896\" width=780 height=438 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4030000/extras/a3f717b8902b9aeee5657d6b1b57877e.webm?t=1772762896\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4030000/extras/a3f717b8902b9aeee5657d6b1b57877e.mp4?t=1772762896\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>", "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In a zombie-ravaged apocalypse where civilization has collapsed, you stand as humanity’s last surviving man—bearing the only cure within you: your potent seed. Alongside a group of alluring survivors, you must fight to endure in this action-packed survival shooter. Battle the undead, protect your companions, and let desire and desperation intertwine as every choice you make shapes humanity’s final chance at survival.</p><h2 c